It should format a string partial
{%- include 'partial' -%}

It should format a variable partial
{% include partial_name %}

It should format a dot-access variable partial
{% include obj.path %}

It should format a bracket-access variable partial
{% include hash.key %}

It should format alias-only
{% include 'partial' as foo %}

It should format variable with alias
{% include partial_name as foo %}

It should break on named args
printWidth: 1
{% include 'partial',
  key1: val1,
  key2: (0..1)
%}

It should format variable partial with named args
{% include partial_name, key1: val1, key2: 'hi' %}

It should format variable with expression and alias
{% include partial_name with 'value' as foo %}

It should not require commas (as per syntax) but add them when pretty printed
{% include 'partial', key1: val1, key2: (0..1) %}

It should strip trailing commas by default
{% include 'partial' %}
{% include 'partial', product: product %}
